String length: 11
Original string: java programming
Uppercase string: JAVA PROGRAMMING
Lowercase string: java programming
Original string: apple
Substring from index 1 to 4: ppl
Original string: The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
Contains 'fox'?: true
Contains 'cat'?: false
```

